r />\n<br />\n我都係咁認為<br />\n垃圾國家請我都唔撚去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去咗怕分分鐘一去冇回頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好怕去<br />\n真係死咗都唔知咩事<br />\n我條女就好想去<br />\n我話佢<br />\n佢就屌返我轉頭<br />\n話咩佢自己有自由<br />\n佢會為自己條命負責<br />\n講極唔聽<br />\n我都唔知點算<br />\n女人聽下其他人講好正就話要去<br />\n自己條仔講嘅嘢就聽唔入耳<br />\n下下就話人管住佢<br />\n唔係話歧視<br />\n但九成女人都係咁撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbff60c121731095db90dbc7725612957b38a40","tid":113462,"uid":68407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:46:49.000Z","msg":"佢有時會打上網台講鬼故<br />\n不過我都信佢係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到佢出返黎已經60歲<br />\n成世冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3f20385c10e8f441afa068401b4b65cb102464","tid":113462,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:16:02.000Z","msg":"黑社會，死不足惜"},{"pid":"b28f4e7ff1fb6a1a4ef9a9cd299975e15a9e98cf","tid":113462,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:20:00.000Z","msg":"地獄鬼國"},{"pid":"b473a69f6e06ae77410c0377923b84e8b4486fa5","tid":113462,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:20:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73950eee82efe0edaed926fb74687d45ca503c8d","tid":113462,"uid":56720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:30:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd5a89066d6e70697f37526bb32aa00bf6116e19","tid":113462,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127cbda306cf71eebb1e9c9048531642c5109719","tid":113462,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:54:39.000Z","msg":"So"},{"pid":"6725e421c88d44c0cc26eac0c9cdcafeba3f4701","tid":113462,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58c9ddf0da07a565e2b09657caf049febaf8ccf","tid":113462,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"失戀去菲律賓散心"},{"pid":"7403834510a8093e5000dbcd44d561c9caf3444f","tid":113462,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:16:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb0c3dd3ce61034e55dc09a32cc9b9b00ac90064","tid":113462,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:06:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df8a0120c4a5f11a570834b831658b492c519581","tid":113462,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:08:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8a61cfd72ff7fa997fe3676fcb826d2f65e03b9","tid":113462,"uid":75221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T19:31:23.000Z","msg":"好多人問，佢屋企人呢 乜乜物物。<br />\n如果有睇開佢就知，佢老豆係警長黎 03年吞槍自殺因為債務問題。果陣上左2日a1 ，話係細佬爛賭加上佢又坐監。 <br />\n<br />\n佢單案拘留左11年先開審， 犯罪物品又銷哂。 同一個單位拉三個。有個放左，有個死埋。 放左果個竟然事件過左十幾年有證人話佢係街度比人拉，而個官又信。 <br />\n<br />\n好多年，都有立法會議員過去幫佢。 但真係候審太耐。 最近聽強國生環者就話 佢今次上訴等左5年都未有消息，上訴係唔洗個犯去答辯，痴9線，等個官判。 <br />\n<br />\n菲律賓呢d垃圾國家， 證係聽制度都覺得荒謬。<br />\n之前90年代區永祥咪又係比人砌，坐成五年先番到黎仲要港督出面先假釋到。  臨走仲要比人屈多9000hkd ，放佢既理由係冇係拘捕之前讀出宣條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我選擇信佢， 佢其中一個心願係就算判有罪都比佢番香港繼續服刑。 果度一開眼就用錢，根本就貪污腐敗垃圾國家，番到黎我唸都幾渺茫。"},{"pid":"335870d6a90ebc5feda8d33a53ccdfaf55743c48","tid":113462,"uid":14905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T23:39:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9ca4e97cdcc126dad3069b3116bcb628ad50442","tid":113462,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T01:16:41.000Z","msg":"永遠黑色旅遊警示"},{"pid":"f3c9b7bb173aa90a013206db246b196d68b6f